  "general_information": "The INDUSTRIAL COURAGE is a heavy-lift vessel built by Guangzhou Wenchong Shipyard in China. It has an overall length of 99.99m, beam of 20.5m, and maximum draught of 8.3m. The vessel is designed for operation in the Saint Lawrence, Welland Canal, and US Great Lakes, with a heavy lifting ability of 300t achieved by using two cranes located on the port side. It has a total TEU capacity of 431, with 249 TEUs on deck and 182 in holds.",
